-- Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya slump 10 percent at open
-- By Ayla Jean Yackley
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 02:45AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 17 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS>, an Islamic finance institution, slumped 10 percent at the stock market's open to 0.72 lira ($0.33) on Wednesday, extending its losses.

